## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   {{config.packageManager}} install
   ```

2. Start development servers:
   ```bash
   {{config.packageManager}} run dev
   ```

   This will start:
   - Frontend: http://localhost:3000
   - Backend: http://localhost:3001

